e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:13:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c106273a238c71c470dee08ff6c8f3b879eca9b","tid":1235791,"uid":262030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36a75898d392390c479ee9a6a9fe2270b8441783","tid":1235791,"uid":160605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"林夕都出聲，香港班歌星偽人認真垃圾"},{"pid":"ae7017495eabcc9c98156f4af0aae8682a66cfd5","tid":1235791,"uid":7079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a75898d392390c479ee9a6a9fe2270b8441783","tid":1235791,"uid":160605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"林夕都出聲，香港班歌星偽人認真垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲都會表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660376f0126c6eec93768a445f92824504fd673d","tid":1235791,"uid":45120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"寫首歌俾反送中就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cca65908f5624b4afa575c30597f08e933b65fd","tid":1235791,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"745a8ba29294eab76010a00e34378f9d7ac3f8aa","tid":1235791,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"好嘅表達 夕爺作咁多好歌 連飛來飛去都有聽㗎"},{"pid":"f309f686fabae3a3c90f0d891b3c17f673f79594","tid":1235791,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e507c108619ceb411034e39257994cef92c648b","tid":1235791,"uid":135158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"冷血是冷血者的胭脂水粉<br />\n<br />\n熱血是熱血者的生理鹽水<br />\n<br />\n當雨傘用來擋煙霧<br />\n<br />\n口罩用來防催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n不必催了<br />\n<br />\n如果還有淚<br />\n<br />\n早已滾燙成汗 衝擊成血<br />\n<br />\n被可恥迫出來的驕傲<br />\n<br />\n可悲不足以形容<br />\n<br />\n銘刻了一百萬人的名字<br />\n<br />\n鋪滿蛇一般蜿蜒的路與<br />\n<br />\n出路<br />\n<br />\n一滴滴一粒粒整齊的螻蟻<br />\n<br />\n渺小而偉大<br />\n<br />\n如果鎮壓有天公地義的理由<br />\n<br />\n「暴動」從此就是拔掉長得正直的幼苗<br />\n<br />\n說文明法治不容許暴力<br />\n<br />\n但暴力的法治凌辱文明<br />\n<br />\n如果撐傘有罪<br />\n<br />\n對抗暴雨更有必要<br />\n<br />\n的確極度遺憾<br />\n<br />\n在天堂預留的位置上<br />\n<br />\n給了第一個隨香港命運墜下的生命<br />\n<br />\n安息了<br />\n<br />\n而不是早已蒙主寵召<br />\n<br />\n靈魂不曉得賣給了誰的那誰<br />\n<br />\n打吧追吧搜吧封吧抓吧逮吧捕吧微笑吧<br />\n<br />\n你覺得天佑誰來呢<br />\n<br />\n耶穌並沒有下來見你<br />\n<br />\n你有你謙卑而開放<br />\n<br />\n而我們陌生的香港<br />\n<br />\n有永遠熟悉的香港人<br />\n<br />\n永遠爭取「 」<br />\n<br />\n阿門<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n（今天開半邊天窗說亮話，因為非痛心疾首足以言喻。） </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190617/20705602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F20705602&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=9b2c1f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F20705602&h=a9567157\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190617/20705602</a>"},{"pid":"c94313cdeb6225d8baebd15bcd3f5cf621262b0a","tid":1235791,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T21:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f400133d0d63a187b2eceacb216ab5f7784d6d","tid":1235791,"uid":177856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36a75898d392390c479ee9a6a9fe2270b8441783","tid":1235791,"uid":160605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"林夕都出聲，香港班歌星偽人認真垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T21:30:33.000Z","msg":"之前首撐起雨傘都係佢同pan填詞"